###
# MCP Janus Proxy Server - REST API Tests
# Use REST Client extension in VS Code to execute these requests
###

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8443
@httpsUrl = https://localhost:8443
@proxyUrl = {{baseUrl}}

### Variables for OAuth flow
@clientId = test-client-123
@redirectUri = http://localhost:8080/callback
@state = random-state-string-123
@codeVerifier = dBjftJeZ4CVP-mB92K27uhbUJU1p1r_wW1gFWFOEjXk
@authCode = test-auth-code-456
@accessToken = test-opaque-token.base64nonce.base64tag
@refreshToken = test-refresh-token-789

###############################################################################
# Health & Metadata Endpoints
###############################################################################

### Health Check
GET {{proxyUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Protected Resource Metadata (RFC 9728)
GET {{proxyUrl}}/.well-known/oauth-protected-resource
Accept: application/json

###

###############################################################################
# OAuth Authorization Flow
###############################################################################

### Step 1: Initiate Authorization (Authorization Code + PKCE)
POST {{proxyUrl}}/auth/authorize
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

response_type=code
&client_id={{clientId}}
&redirect_uri={{redirectUri}}
&state={{state}}
&code_challenge=E9Melhoa2OwvFrEMTJguCHaoeK1t8URWbuGJSstw-cM
&code_challenge_method=S256
&scope=mcp:read mcp:write
&resource=https://mcp.example.com

###

### Step 2: OAuth Callback (simulated - normally called by auth server)
GET {{proxyUrl}}/auth/callback?code={{authCode}}&state={{state}}

###

### Step 3: Token Exchange
POST {{proxyUrl}}/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=authorization_code
&code={{authCode}}
&redirect_uri={{redirectUri}}
&client_id={{clientId}}
&code_verifier={{codeVerifier}}

###

### Token Exchange - Refresh Token
POST {{proxyUrl}}/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=refresh_token
&refresh_token={{refreshToken}}
&client_id={{clientId}}

###

### Token Exchange - Client Credentials (service-to-service)
POST {{proxyUrl}}/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials
&client_id={{clientId}}
&client_secret=test-secret
&scope=mcp:read mcp:write

###

###############################################################################
# MCP Proxy Requests (Authenticated)
###############################################################################

### MCP Request - List Tools (with valid token)
GET {{proxyUrl}}/mcp/tools
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### MCP Request - Call Tool (with valid token)
POST {{proxyUrl}}/mcp/tools/execute
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "example-tool",
  "arguments": {
    "param1": "value1",
    "param2": "value2"
  }
}

###

### MCP Request - List Resources
GET {{proxyUrl}}/mcp/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### MCP Request - Get Resource
GET {{proxyUrl}}/mcp/resources/example-resource
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### MCP Request - List Prompts
GET {{proxyUrl}}/mcp/prompts
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### MCP Request - Execute Prompt
POST {{proxyUrl}}/mcp/prompts/execute
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "example-prompt",
  "arguments": {
    "context": "test context"
  }
}

###

###############################################################################
# Error Cases & Security Tests
###############################################################################

### MCP Request - No Authorization Header (should fail with 401)
GET {{proxyUrl}}/mcp/tools
Accept: application/json

###

### MCP Request - Invalid Token (should fail with 401)
GET {{proxyUrl}}/mcp/tools
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token-format
Accept: application/json

###

### MCP Request - Malformed Token (should fail with 401)
GET {{proxyUrl}}/mcp/tools
Authorization: Bearer malformed.token.here
Accept: application/json

###

### MCP Request - Expired Token (should fail with 401)
GET {{proxyUrl}}/mcp/tools
Authorization: Bearer expired.token.abc123.def456
Accept: application/json

###

### Token Exchange - Missing Parameters (should fail with 400)
POST {{proxyUrl}}/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=authorization_code

###

### Token Exchange - Invalid Grant Type (should fail with 400)
POST {{proxyUrl}}/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=invalid_grant
&code={{authCode}}

###

### Authorization - Missing PKCE (should fail with 400)
POST {{proxyUrl}}/auth/authorize
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

response_type=code
&client_id={{clientId}}
&redirect_uri={{redirectUri}}
&state={{state}}

###

### Authorization - Invalid Code Challenge Method (should fail with 400)
POST {{proxyUrl}}/auth/authorize
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

response_type=code
&client_id={{clientId}}
&redirect_uri={{redirectUri}}
&state={{state}}
&code_challenge=test-challenge
&code_challenge_method=plain

###

